									<h2 class=vol-title">Mind: What Is It? </h2>
									<img src="http://local.prosperitybible.com/sites/all/themes/vanzen/images/vol-2-1-img.jpg" class="inline-left" title="Mind: What Is It? " alt="Mind: What Is It? " height="235" width="300"/>
									<p class="regular">The Law of Attraction teaches us that, as a first step, we must positively will what we Desire so as to set in motion the Universal Forces that will attract our Desire to us. This is often accomplished by taking the first practical step of surrounding ourselves with the right people – those people in harmony with what it is that we Desire. In this series of articles by Mr. Wattles, you will learn how to use your Mind to present yourself in the proper and necessary role as a leader so that you may attract others who seek the leadership you possess.&nbsp; Think about it: if wealth is what you Desire, you would much rather want to attract to you wealthy people than those who live in poverty.</p>
									<p class="regular">Our habits, conditioning and paradigms determine how we live our lives from day-to-day; but, what we fail to realize is that HOW we spend our days, leads to HOW we spend our weeks, months and years. Thus, by CHANGING our habits, conditioning and paradigms of how we view our world, we have the God-given Power and Ability to CHANGE Our World! We were given an infinitely POWERFUL Mind – as standard operating equipment at birth – and we can use it – TODAY – to alter our conditioning, eliminate bad habits, and change our paradigms and spend more of our energy on what leads us TOWARDS what it is that we Desire, rather than away from it.</p>
									<p class="regular">We engage in various mental activities virtually non-stop – from true conscious deep thinking to mindless daydreaming.. Now imagine the incredible Power of aligning your mental activities towards purposeful, directed and focused thinking – all directed towards a specific objective, With these teachings, You will learn to do just that and leverage the Infinite Power of YOUR Mind.</p>									

									<div id="divider"> 
										<img src="http://local.prosperitybible.com/sites/all/themes/vanzen/images/divider.png" /> 
									</div><!-- #divider close -->	
									
									<ul class="tick">
										<li>Understand Your Mind, how it functions and HOW to tap the infinite abilities inherent within Your Conscious and Subconscious Minds</li>
										<li>How the Mind is the seat of the Life-Force and directs every voluntary and involuntary function of the physical body, including behavior, actions and results (cause and effect).</li>
										<li>Understand Thinking and the Thought processes of the Mind; Learn to Develop and Use TRUE Thought (Purposeful Thinking), and not be a captive to the Default Mode of random, purposeless thinking.</li>
										<li>Learn to engage in consistent, sustained and concentrated thought – the key ingredient necessary to attain Wealth and Success at any level and in any endeavor.</li>
										<li>Learn to focus the unlimited and infinite powers of the mind towards any objective.</li>
										<li>Understand the powerful storage abilities of the mind and learn to cultivate that potent function to fulfill your Desires and attain the Wealth and Success You deserve.</li>
										<li>Using the powerhouse of the Mind to overcome ANY bad habit by changing past, faulty conditioning to proper, effective and controlling conditioning to serve You (and NOT vice versa!)</li>
										<li>Don’t be controlled by Your past or present events and circumstances; learn to utilize Your Conscious and Subconscious Mind to reprogram Your conditioning so that YOU control YOUR life.</li>
										<li>Overcome Victim Consciousness, design YOUR life and control the events and circumstances of today and tomorrow.</li>
										<li>Learn to activate and utilize the “dormant” portions of the Mind – that YOU don’t even know exist!</li>
										<li>Overcome bad habits and replace them with good habits – easily, effectively and permanently.</li>
										<li>Understand the differences between “wanting” and “willing” and how to tap the Power of the Will to accomplish ANY goal and overcome ANY challenge or obstacle.</li>
										<li>Learn to harness the Power of Desire and stoke it to a cogent, burning force that will propel You towards ANY Goal and magnetically attract that Goal towards You.</li>
										<li>Use the infinite Power of the Mind to develop strong, well-defined and attractive Character that automatically captivates the attention of others.</li>
										<li>Learn to use the Mind to educe Your natural, inherent and latent leadership attributes so that others will seek You as a leader in any endeavor.</li>
									</ul>
									
