									<h2 class=vol-title">Lessons In Constructive Science</h2>
									<img src="http://local.prosperitybible.com/sites/all/themes/vanzen/images/vol-2-3-img.jpg" class="inline-left" title="Lessons In Constructive Science" alt="Lessons In Constructive Science" height="235" width="300" />
									<p class="regular">God wants us all to Live an Abundant, Prosperous and Wealthy life - whether financial or otherwise. It is Nature’s intent that ALL things – and most particularly, human life – GROW.  The purpose of Nature is the advancement and unfoldment of life and Desire is possibility seeking expression, or function seeking performance.</p>
									<p class="regular">In this series of fifteen Lessons, you will learn to distinguish between merely wanting (wishing) and Willing (Desiring) in order to focus your mental, emotional and spiritual being to be receptive to only that which you truly Desire through use and application of proven Constructive Science methods.</p>
									<p class="regular">“As a man thinketh in his heart, so shall he be.”  Under the Laws of the Universe, we inherently attract what we think. When we think negatively, we focus upon that which we don’t want, thereby attracting the very thing that we FEAR and NOT what we want; likewise, when we think positively, and focus upon our true Desires, we thereby attract that which we seek.  In Lessons in Constructive Science, you will learn HOW maximize your positive Mental Attitude to cultivate and exploit YOUR God-given abilities and transform YOUR thought processes into real, tangible RESULTS.</p>
									<p class="regular">Learning to distinguish between Constructive and Destructive Mental Attitudes will change the way YOU think.  Changing the WAY YOU THINK will change the RESULTS in YOUR Life.</p>
									
									<div id="divider"> 
										<img src="http://local.prosperitybible.com/sites/all/themes/vanzen/images/divider.png" /> 
									</div><!-- #divider close -->	
									
									<ul class="tick">
										<li>What is Constructive Science of the Mind and how is it used.</li>
										<li>What constitutes Constructive Speech (vs. Destructive Speech) and why it is important to leading a full life and attaining Success and Prosperity.</li>
										<li>Learn Constructive Speech to cultivate relationships with others, win friends – and influence people!</li>
										<li>How Constructive Speech develops Constructive Thought – a fundamental element towards creating the life You Desire and Deserve.</li>
										<li>Why Constructive Speech is necessary to maintaining a positive outlook and overcoming faulty conditioning and negative habits.</li>
										<li>How to use Constructive Speech and right talk to build Wealth and attain Prosperity.</li>
										<li>Learn to overcome Intellectual Laziness to generate Wealth and Riches.</li>
										<li>Using Constructive Speech to eliminate Poverty Consciousness and replace it with Prosperity Consciousness.</li>
										<li>The “connection” between Constructive Speech and good Health and why what you say may be bad for your Health.</li>
										<li>The “sympathy habit” – what it is, why it is so destructive, and why it is hard to break.</li>
										<li>How to “sympathize health” when afflicted with poor health, so as to gain good Health.</li>
										<li>The effect of “stressful” or agitating work on Your Health and how to adopt habits and methods to override such destructive effects on Body, Mind and Spirit.</li>
										<li>“Hate Thought” – what is it and why You must rid it completely from your Conscious and Subconscious Mind.</li>
										<li>The deleterious and extremely powerful impact of “Hate Thought” and why “it is just as disastrous to hate THINGS as it is to hate people.”</li>
										<li>How to adopt the Constructive Attitude and use it to achieve Good in all aspects of life and Success in any endeavor.</li>
										<li>“Image Making” – the scientific method of Constructive Visualization and a fundamental step in the process of attaining the Good that You Desire in Your Life.</li>
										<li>Why (and how) “living cheaply” fails to attract Prosperity and continues the cycle of Poverty Consciousness.</li>
										<li>“Conspicuous Waste” – what it is and why it is to be avoided in order to attract Prosperity, Abundance and Wealth.</li>
										<li>How to dismiss the Thought Habit that You “cannot afford” what you want in Life and that by “learning to talk wealth, health and progress, you can have the best of everything.”</li>
										<li>Why being “economic” and “thrifty” and “living cheaply” actually impedes the flow of Wealth, Abundance and Prosperity.</li>
										<li>Understanding Your God-given abilities to achieve Prosperity and attain Success of ANY nature, level and extent and how to harness and utilize those abilities. (“Differences in ability are not differences in faculty, but in the development of faculty . . .&nbsp; And since there is no faculty which cannot be developed, there is nothing in the way of ability which is impossible to any man.”)</li>
										<li>Constructive vs. Destructive Mental Attitudes – how to recognize the differences by paying attention to Your thought processes.</li>
										<li>The Power of Faith in attaining Success in any endeavor.</li>
										<li>“The Matter of Attitude” – Your own Mental Attitude towards Your own Abilities and why cultivating the proper Mental Attitude is critical to exploiting Your Abilities to their highest levels.</li>
										<li>Why “Desire, in itself, has no power to bring you what you want,” but how Desire may be utilized to fuel scientific methods for attaining that which is Desired.</li>
										<li>How to “mentally unite” Yourself to that which you Desire in order to manifest the Desired subject in the physical world.</li>
										<li>Desire is the Mental Force that connects You to and moves you towards the object of Desire; Expectation is the complimentary Mental Force that moves the object of Desire towards You.</li>
										<li>The Power of Visualization (Image Making) and why You should NEVER Visualize that which you do not Desire.</li>
										<li>Your Attitude towards those opposed to Your Beliefs: Living Your Beliefs vs. attempting to convert others to Your Beliefs – knowing the difference between the two and why it matters.</li>
										<li>Developing a Great Character – why it is important to achieving Success.</li>
										<li>The importance of “Mental Cooperation” with others and why it is critical to proper Living and attaining Prosperity and achieving Spiritual, Emotional and Financial Success (“Affirm for all, desire for all, work for all and know and feel that you are one with all.&nbsp; In unity is strength.”)</li>
										<li>Overcome the fear of spending money by understanding that the concepts of lack and limitation are merely limiting beliefs and that You are surrounded by Infinite Abundance and Prosperity.</li>
										<li>Learn how to place Your Mental, Emotional and Spiritual Being in a “State of Receptivity” so that you may manifest in the physical world the Good that you Desire and Deserve.</li>
										<li>The Power of Personality – what it is and what it means to true Love.</li>
										<li>Ideals and how to form them (“Ideals” are Ideas that You fall in love with).</li>
										<li>Why the Desire to Live Abundantly is not only normal, but necessary for a full, rich and Spiritual Life.</li>
										<li>Learn to recognize (and understand) the fundamental differences between selfishness/greed vs. abundance/wealth/prosperity and why the latter is congruent with God’s intentions for man, while the former constitutes sin.</li>
										<li>Why You must first attain Wealth and Prosperity (if not Financially, at least Spiritually) before you may become of true, charitable service to others.</li>
									<ul>						
			
