									<h2 class=vol-title">What Is Truth?</h2>
									<img src="http://local.prosperitybible.com/sites/all/themes/vanzen/images/vol-2-3-img.jpg" class="inline-left" title="What Is Truth?" alt="What Is Truth?" height="235" width="300"/>	
									<p class="regular">We all have it and most of us waste it: Time. In What Is Truth?, Wattles teaches his philosophy on the nature of&nbsp; space, matter and, yes, time and our role in the Universe as a whole.</p>
									<p class="regular">As Infinite as the Universe, so too is our Consciousness and the Powers and Abilities of our Mind. In What Is Truth? learn HOW these Universal Truths translate into Infinite possibilities for YOU, and, consequently, for what YOU hold to be possible for YOUR Life – Spiritually, Emotionally, Intellectually, and Financially.</p>
									<p class="regular">YOU were created in the likeness and image of God with the inherent ability to co-create YOUR Life! As a Spiritual Being, with an Intelligent Mind and Powerful Conscious Ability, does this not also suggest that God provide YOU with an INFINITE CREATIVE POWER?&nbsp; Learning to tap into this Self-Supremacy will not only bring YOU closer to our Supreme Intelligence and Creator, but will you to access YOUR God-given abilities to be, do and have more – to attain the Life that YOU Desire!</p>
									
									<div id="divider"> 
										<img src="http://local.prosperitybible.com/sites/all/themes/vanzen/images/divider.png" /> 
									</div><!-- #divider close -->	

									<ul class="tick">
										<li>Understanding “Time” and how to work in accordance with Universal Laws.</li>
										<li>Understanding concepts of “Space” and “Matter” from a fundamental metaphysical perspective.</li>
										<li>What is “Substance,” “Original/One Substance” and “One Changeless Substance” and how all Desires are manifested through Impression by Mind in Substance.</li>
										<li>The One Creative Intelligence/Consciousness of God and the Consciousness of the Mind of man explained; that the Consciousness of Man seeks unification with the Consciousness of Its Creator (Creative Intelligence).</li>
										<li>Understand the Infiniteness of Your Conscious and Subconscious Mind and that there is no limitation to Your Abilities.</li>
										<li>Understanding “Motion” and the spatial relationships of Time, Space and Matter explained.</li>
										<li>“Force,” “Vibration” and “Attraction” explained on a fundamental level with respect to the Law of Mental Force, Law of Vibration and Law of Attraction.</li>
										<li>Man and His Power: Man is created in the Likeness and Image of God, and thus, has inherent, God-given Powers and Abilities. Within our Minds, we all possess Infinite Powers and Abilities that came as standard operating equipment at birth.</li>
										<li>Self-Supremacy: What it means and why God intended all man and woman to be Great and bestowed with Abundance and Prosperity.</li>
										<li>“The solution of man’s problems of health, wealth, and growth can be reached when man unifies himself with God, the Great Intelligent Spirit, Substance, who seeks life and happiness in man; and man can unify himself with God only by constantly recognizing God; by considering and acknowledging God, and by looking to God in prayer.”</li>
									</ul>									
	
