									<h2 class=vol-title">The Personal Power Course</h2>
									<img src="http://local.prosperitybible.com/sites/all/themes/vanzen/images/vol-2-4-img.jpg" class="inline-left" title="The Personal Power Course" alt="The Personal Power Course" height="235" width="300"/>
									
									<div id="divider"> 
										<img src="http://local.prosperitybible.com/sites/all/themes/vanzen/images/divider.png" /> 
									</div><!-- #divider close -->	

									<ul class="tick">
										<li>The Physical Side of Health-Culture: Establishing Perfect Digestion and assimilation for a healthy body.</li>
										<li>How proper meal planning and eating and maintaining the necessary Mental Attitude results in Perfect Digestion.</li>
										<li>The lost practice of Fletcherism: What it is and how it works to establish Perfect Digestion, good Health and proper body composition and weight.</li>
										<li>How proper Breathing promotes good Health and can be used to overcome sickness, ailments and general poor Health.</li>
										<li>The Mental Side of Health-Culture: How the Subconscious Mind directs the Life Force of the Body from a systemic to cellular level.</li>
										<li>Why “sickness and low states of Health can only be cured by arousing the Subconscious Mind to Constructive Activity.”</li>
										<li>How to arouse the Subconscious Mind to Constructive Activity to build and maintain strong, vigorous Health.</li>
										<li>“If your subconscious mind is aroused into Constructive Activity, it will cure you, and keep you cured.”</li>
										<li>“If the inner Mind is to be aroused into Constructive Activity, the activities of the outer Mind must become constructive.”</li>
										<li>How to build and maintain Constructive Activity in the objective Conscious Mind in order to establish, build and maintain Constructive Activity in the subjective Subconscious Mind.</li>
										<li>“When you have acquired the habit of thinking and speaking Construction, and nothing but Construction, you have mastered Mental Science, in so far as Health is concerned.”</li>
										<li>Using the “light breakfast” or “no breakfast” plan to energize Your day and foster strong Physical and Mental Health.</li>
										<li>The Physical Side of Wealth-Culture: Building a strong financial structure by assimilating Wealth.</li>
										<li>Why You MUST use BOTH Your Creative Power AND Your Assimilative Power to create and retain Wealth.</li>
										<li>How Wealth may be further generated by Constructive use of existing Wealth.</li>
										<li>Why the attainment of Wealth is a function of exact use of scientific Laws.</li>
										<li>Learn the processes of generating Wealth from the Original Substance.</li>
										<li>“Wealth-culture consists in making constructive use of all the people and things with which you are brought into association in your business or profession.”</li>
										<li>Why choosing the business or profession that suits Your tastes is the best course of action to attaining honest and lasting Wealth.</li>
										<li>“Nothing is more certain than that you can be what you want to be, in the matter of talent and ability; and if that is true, it is also certain that you can do what you want to do.”</li>
										<li>The Power of taking immediate ACTION, coupled with Faith (“When you move forward with full faith, every act becomes a success in itself, being done in the spirit of success; and the only way to achieve complete success in life is to make every act a success in itself.”)</li>
										<li>Learn the simple basic rules for achieving Success in any endeavor, at any level.</li>
										<li>The Mental Side of Wealth Culture: Why the attainment of Wealth requires the proper use of Constructive Thought congruent with the Laws of Nature.</li>
										<li>Why Nature intends that ALL Life live for fullest expression and Growth.</li>
										<li>How to eliminate doubt and replace it with Knowledge and Faith that You will Attain the Wealth that You Desire and Deserve.</li>
										<li>Learn how to remove, or use to Your advantage, Obstacles that seemingly prevent You from attaining Wealth.</li>
										<li>How to Develop Your Talents: How to develop Your latent or hidden talents that may best serve You in achieving Your objectives and attaining Success in what You Desire.</li>
										<li>How to develop talents and abilities in any area to generate Power through proper programming of the Subconscious Mind.</li>
										<li>How to exercise various faculties of the Mind to cultivate and strengthen Your Powers and Abilities.</li>
										<li>How to tap the limitless and infinite resources of the Universal Mind for Your Mental Development.</li>
										<li>Developing patience to achieve perfection.</li>
										<li>The Retention of Youth: How to stay Young in Body, Mind and Spirit.</li>
										<li>Using the Subconscious Mind to renew and regenerate a more Youthful body at the cellular level.</li>
										<li>How the use of improper speech and Thought ages the Body.</li>
										<li>“To retain youth, man must think continually and only of the processes of renewal as going on within his body; he must not, for an instant give thought and attention to the processes of destruction.”</li>
										<li>Growing older vs. Living longer – how Your paradigm (viewpoint) actually regulates the aging process.</li>
										<li>Marital Happiness: How to recreate original marital bliss.</li>
										<li>Why true love is the most powerful factor to attaining true happiness – more than Health, Wealth or Success.</li>
										<li>Why Love is ALWAYS won, or attracted by the person who is beloved.</li>
										<li>Making Constructive use of the Power of Personality to win Love.</li>
										<li>Winning Love: “Be what you are; and if you are not enough to win love, be more; develop yourself.”</li>
										<li>Learn the Key to finding Love: “If you wish to be loved, you must live your own life; and the fuller and more complete the life, the more love you will win.”</li>
										<li>Learn how to revitalize Your Marriage by making the most of who You are and winning back Love.</li>
										<li>Why Marital Happiness is a function of continued Courtship.</li>
										<li>Opportunity: Understanding that there is NO limit to Opportunity; the ONLY limits are those that we place upon ourselves and carry in the Mind.</li>
										<li>Why faulty belief as to a “lack” of Opportunity suppresses Faith and prevents Growth and Advancement.</li>
										<li>Restriction of Opportunity vs. Lack of Opportunity: Knowing the differences and why it is critical to Your Success.</li>
										<li>How to use Infinite Intelligence to reveal true Opportunity.</li>
										<li>How to overcome obstacles and actually use them to pursue Opportunity.</li>
										<li>Why Harmony with Infinite Intelligence is absolutely necessary for certainty of Success (the “Harmonious Law of Attraction”).</li>
										<li>Recognizing right Constructive Action vs. ordinary action and why it is necessary shorten the time necessary to attain various levels of Success.</li>
									</ul>								
							
